data.title: Book A Private Rental – Jabbers Play
data.text:
Private Party Rental $349

All members* receive a 10% discount

*Membership must be held by birthday child

What’s included: Admission for all guests, private use of our entire facility for 2 hours, set up and clean up, decorations set up, tablecloths, plates, napkins, and utensils. Private rentals are also allowed to bring ANY outside food or drink, excluding any glass containers on the main floor.

*Party themes available for an additional cost

Private Party times are available Monday-Sunday 7-9pm and Sundays at 10am-12pm. Please submit requests for additional/special time slots by emailing jabbersllc@gmail.com.

*An additional $50 is charged for every 30-minutes past 9pm.

Please select your preferred date for your Private Rental. After you click submit, proceed to the next step after submission to provide us with more details and pay a $50 deposit to hold your time slot.

*Parties must be booked 48 hours in advanced. If you would like to book a party less than 48 hours, you must get an approval by management by submitting a quick contact (email) or calling in.*
